Apt 415 has beautiful views of the community and mountains with a large private patio.  This apartment is the last one left with a bathtub!  All our apartment homes have AC units and private patios!  Come tour today you dont want to miss out on this one. <br>
<br>
Schedule an in-person or virtual tour today!<br>
Call or text:  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/pdx/apa/7516087395/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
<br>
<br>
Check out our Website: https://solacepdx.com/<br>
Check out our Instagram: @solaceapartments<br>
Check out our YouTube Channel: Solace Apartments<br>
<br>
Apartment Features:<br>
*East facing<br>
*Kitchen Storage<br>
*An in-unit washer and dryer<br>
*Energy efficient stainless-steel appliances<br>
*Gas range<br>
*Air conditioning<br>
*A private balcony<br>
*A floor to ceiling tile shower with a frameless glass door<br>
*White oak flooring<br>
*Quartz countertops with tile back splashes<br>
*Oversized window<br>
*Bright living space<br>
<br>
Community Features:<br>
*Gated parking<br>
*Secure access to the building<br>
*24-hour state of the art gym<br>
*24-hour free gourmet coffee in our lobby<br>
*A bike storage room with assisted lift bike racks, a fix-it station, gear lockers, a bike shower, and a hydration station<br>
*Two rooftop terraces with a lounging area, fire table, grill, and a beautiful view of Mt. Hood<br>
*Community room with flat screen TV, Kitchen, and double-sided fireplace<br>
*Free Wi-Fi in all common areas<br>
*Onsite maintenance<br>
*Leasing office open 7 days a week<br>
*Walk score of 93 and a bike score of 100. We are only a short walk away from New Seasons Market, Legacy Emanuel Medical Center, and a wide selection of restaurants, food trucks, and shops.<br>
<br>
Application fee: $59/applicant<br>
Security deposit: $0 upon approved credit<br>
Parking: 200/month<br>
Pet deposit:$500/pet<br>
Pet rent:$50/pet/month<br>
Pet weight limit: 50 lbs.<br>
(Breed restrictions apply)<br>
